Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • uni.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Student>, IStudent

    public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStudent
    Student is a person attending classes at University.

    The Student class creates objects which are represented by name, surname, number of index and a grade.
